abel___bOW_ pill-label">Connect Your Tools</span></div><div class="ExpandablePill_pillContent__oodmL pill-content"><p>Everything plays together. Your agents plug directly into your existing apps and data so they have the full context from day one.</p></div></div><div class="ExpandablePill_expandablePill__Cmoj5 expandable-pill" data-expandable-pill="true" data-visual-id="direct-message"><div class="ExpandablePill_pillHeader__8RX0u pill-header"><img src="images/chat-bubble.svg" alt="/images/chat-bubble.svg" class="ExpandablePill_pillIcon__VxOcI pill-icon" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><span class="ExpandablePill_pillLabel___bOW_ pill-label">Sync Humans &amp; Agents</span></div><div class="ExpandablePill_pillContent__oodmL pill-content"><p>Build your dream team. Seamlessly pair human intuition with AI muscle, assigning specific tasks to the "brain" best suited for the job.</p></div></div><div class="ExpandablePill_expandablePill__Cmoj5 expandable-pill" data-expandable-pill="true" data-visual-id="assign-task"><div class="ExpandablePill_pillHeader__8RX0u pill-header"><img src="images/add-task.svg" alt="/images/add-task.svg" class="ExpandablePill_pillIcon__VxOcI pill-icon" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><span class="ExpandablePill_pillLabel___bOW_ pill-label">Learn &amp; Adapt</span></div><div class="ExpandablePill_pillContent__oodmL pill-content"><p>They get smarter as you go. Your agents study your preferences and business quirks, evolving from basic tools into expert teammates.</p></div></div><div class="ExpandablePill_expandablePill__Cmoj5 expandable-pill" data-expandable-pill="true" data-visual-id="schedule-events"><div class="ExpandablePill_pillHeader__8RX0u pill-header"><img src="images/calendar.svg" alt="/images/calendar.svg" class="ExpandablePill_pillIcon__VxOcI pill-icon" loading="lazy" decoding="async"><span class="ExpandablePill_pillLabel___bOW_ pill-label">Total Recall</span></div><div class="ExpandablePill_pillContent__oodmL pill-content"><p>A permanent m